{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And told me, to try to fill out something else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then this might help you, because those we might not take or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So here I was with a new name, making new friends, facing a new challenge under this new name as a Pole, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And nobody uncovered at the time a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it's things like that which gave me confidence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, at one point I got into a certain business venture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This person who, where I lived, had friends in the refinery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were working in an asphalt pit, where he was buying asphalt for them for this factory where he was working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, at that point, had a job which I got through the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I got a regular job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the course of that job, I met a man from Warsaw who was very much interested in buying this kind of asphalt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I organized a system whereby through his contacts, I would be getting that asphalt from the refinery, sort of like a black market operation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because, by the way, the Germans would not allow the Poles to buy anything officially or legitimately.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only way they could live is only through the black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everything was on the black market.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole economy was geared that everybody would steal part of what he was involved, to the extent that he could, and sell it on the black market.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this case, I organized the stealing of that asphalt, you know, and shipping it to Warsaw, and selling it through that man.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this developed into a quite profitable business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But mostly what I liked about it, it gave me a cover for my existence.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
